  "content": "<blockquote>\n<p class=\"\">If you're considering a premium UK boarding school experience for your child, this is your moment. A <strong>limited-time discount offer</strong> has just been announced for international students applying to one of the <strong>UK's most prestigious and luxurious boarding schools</strong> for the <strong>September 2025 intake</strong>.</p>\n<p class=\"\">This special offer is part of an initiative to make elite British education more accessible for global families, while supporting the work of trusted education partners. Here’s what you need to know:</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>What the Offer Includes</h2>\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-1877\" src=\"https://universitio.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/jobuk-3.jpg\" alt=\"25% off\" width=\"1890\" height=\"796\" />\n<ul>\n        <li class=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><strong>25% Discount on Tuition Fees</strong><br />Applicable for the full duration of all standard 3-term academic courses. <em>(Short-term courses not included.)</em></p>\n</li>\n        <li class=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><strong>10% Discount on Boarding Fees</strong><br />Valid for the <strong>first year of accommodation</strong>, easing the financial commitment of relocating to the UK.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Who Is Eligible?</h2>\n<ul>\n        <li class=\"\">\n<p class=\"\">Students who receive an <strong>offer of admission by 31st May 2025</strong>.</p>\n</li>\n        <li class=\"\">\n<p class=\"\">Students must <strong>accept their offer within 2 weeks</strong> to qualify for the discount.</p>\n</li>\n        <li class=\"\">\n<p class=\"\">The offer also applies to current applicants who are still waiting for a decision.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Why This Matters</h2>\n<p class=\"\">This prestigious school offers not only a <strong>world-class academic environment</strong> but also <strong>state-of-the-art facilities, highly qualified faculty</strong>, and a culturally rich, supportive boarding experience. It's a unique opportunity to access <strong>one of the UK's most luxurious and well-regarded educational institutions</strong>, now with meaningful financial support.</p>\n\n<h2>Take the Next Step</h2>\n<p class=\"\">If you’re looking to provide your child with a top-tier education and unforgettable international experience, we encourage you to apply now. This is a rare chance to enrol at an elite British boarding school with <strong>significant financial savings</strong>.</p>\n<p class=\"\">To get started, contact our admissions team through our website, call us directly, or reach out via WhatsApp on +44 7963 345465. We’re here to guide you every step of the way, or you can <a href=\"https://universitio.com/free-consultation\">book your free consultation session here</a>.</p>"
